#VCT loai bo cac phan tu trong mot danh sach tai cac vi tri index 1, 3, 4 cho truoc
#Red Green Black Pink Yellow ->  Red White Yellow
a=input()
A=a.split()
for i in range(len(A)):
    if i==1 and i==3 and i==4:
        A.remove(A[i])
print(A)
